1
00:00:07,477 --> 00:00:09,017
<b>(Episode 19)</b>

2
00:00:09,017 --> 00:00:10,317
<b>Hello?</b>

3
00:00:11,147 --> 00:00:12,886
<b>Goodness, Director Song!</b>

4
00:00:12,886 --> 00:00:14,347
<b>One second.</b>

5
00:00:14,347 --> 00:00:16,187
<b>What's the occasion?</b>

6
00:00:16,456 --> 00:00:18,316
<b>Wow, it has been so long.</b>

7
00:00:19,056 --> 00:00:20,886
<b>You can hop in first. Go ahead.</b>

8
00:00:22,126 --> 00:00:24,157
<b>It's always the same with us.</b>

9
00:00:44,347 --> 00:00:46,287
<b>Ms. Park will be here
after that phone call.</b>

10
00:00:50,256 --> 00:00:51,317
<b>Okay, sure.</b>

11
00:00:52,627 --> 00:00:53,627
<b>What is this?</b>

12
00:00:54,957 --> 00:00:56,127
<b>Stop that car!</b>

13
00:00:56,226 --> 00:00:58,097
<b>You have to get that car!</b>

14
00:00:58,357 --> 00:00:59,826
<b>- No!
- Wait!</b>

15
00:00:59,826 --> 00:01:02,336
<b>Who do you think you are?</b>

16
00:01:02,436 --> 00:01:04,796
<b>Ha Jin!</b>

17
00:01:14,677 --> 00:01:15,677
<b>Anchor Lee.</b>

18
00:01:15,677 --> 00:01:18,416
<b>Hey. Are you with Ha Jin?</b>

19
00:01:18,416 --> 00:01:20,086
<b>I can't get a hold of her.</b>

20
00:01:21,187 --> 00:01:22,386
<b>She...</b>

21
00:01:23,287 --> 00:01:24,987
<b>She just got abducted.</b>

22
00:01:27,287 --> 00:01:28,356
<b>What?</b>

23
00:01:32,496 --> 00:01:35,327
<b>(Find Me in Your Memory)</b>

24
00:01:50,146 --> 00:01:51,146
<b>Ha Kyung.</b>

25
00:01:52,146 --> 00:01:53,146
<b>Anchor Lee.</b>

26
00:01:54,446 --> 00:01:55,787
<b>What's the situation?</b>

27
00:01:55,787 --> 00:01:58,586
<b>Her phone was turned off
right after the situation broke out,</b>

28
00:01:58,586 --> 00:01:59,687
<b>so we can't track her.</b>

29
00:01:59,687 --> 00:02:01,226
<b>What about her location?</b>

30
00:02:01,226 --> 00:02:02,827
<b>We're tracking down that car.</b>

31
00:02:03,556 --> 00:02:05,996
<b>Are we yet to find out who did this?</b>

32
00:02:05,996 --> 00:02:08,696
<b>We found a security camera nearby
and are looking into it,</b>

33
00:02:08,696 --> 00:02:10,467
<b>but we'll have to see.</b>

34
00:02:10,467 --> 00:02:13,306
<b>And the current suspects,
Ji Hyun Geun and Moon Chul.</b>

35
00:02:13,306 --> 00:02:15,006
<b>We're looking for there whereabouts,</b>

36
00:02:15,006 --> 00:02:16,576
<b>but they're both unreachable.</b>

37
00:02:16,777 --> 00:02:19,176
<b>Goodness, Ha Jin.</b>

38
00:02:19,446 --> 00:02:21,506
<b>- Yes?
- What will happen to her?</b>

39
00:02:21,706 --> 00:02:22,916
<b>You found the car?</b>

40
00:02:23,247 --> 00:02:24,277
<b>Where is it?</b>

41
00:02:32,627 --> 00:02:34,087
<b>- Did you find anything?
- Over here.</b>

42
00:02:39,266 --> 00:02:41,266
<b>I think he changed cars here
and ran away.</b>

43
00:02:43,236 --> 00:02:44,736
<b>Hey. Sir!</b>

44
00:02:44,736 --> 00:02:45,736
<b>What is it?</b>

45
00:02:47,307 --> 00:02:48,407
<b>Darn it.</b>

46
00:02:49,537 --> 00:02:50,537
<b>Hey.</b>

47
00:02:53,446 --> 00:02:54,976
<b>He found a place
with no security camera,</b>

48
00:02:54,976 --> 00:02:56,976
<b>prepared another car to run away in,</b>

49
00:02:56,976 --> 00:02:58,676
<b>and even used anesthetics?</b>

50
00:02:59,046 --> 00:03:01,287
<b>This jerk had this planned.</b>

51
00:03:01,386 --> 00:03:02,386
<b>Take this.</b>

52
00:03:12,527 --> 00:03:14,467
<b>- Yes.
- Where are you?</b>

53
00:03:14,467 --> 00:03:17,097
<b>Do you know what time it is?
Why aren't you at work?</b>

54
00:03:24,777 --> 00:03:25,777
<b>Come in.</b>

55
00:03:28,407 --> 00:03:31,377
<b>What's going on?
Are you coming in just now?</b>

56
00:03:32,446 --> 00:03:35,446
<b>Mr. Kim has been
looking for you everywhere.</b>

57
00:03:35,747 --> 00:03:37,356
<b>I have something to tell you.</b>

58
00:03:37,356 --> 00:03:39,657
<b>What's going on? What is it?</b>

59
00:03:39,657 --> 00:03:41,726
<b>Something happened to Ha Jin.</b>

60
00:03:43,296 --> 00:03:45,256
<b>I think she was
abducted by her stalker.</b>

61
00:03:46,666 --> 00:03:47,666
<b>What?</b>

62
00:03:48,467 --> 00:03:51,497
<b>Are you saying
Ha Jin is abducted right now?</b>

63
00:03:51,497 --> 00:03:53,437
<b>The police are investigating this
behind closed doors.</b>

64
00:03:53,437 --> 00:03:54,867
<b>How long has it been?</b>

65
00:03:55,307 --> 00:03:57,076
<b>Do you have any information?</b>

66
00:03:57,076 --> 00:03:58,476
<b>They're still investigating.</b>

67
00:03:58,476 --> 00:04:00,247
<b>And they don't know
her location yet?</b>

68
00:04:01,006 --> 00:04:02,006
<b>No.</b>

69
00:04:04,747 --> 00:04:06,386
<b>Okay, I understand.</b>

70
00:04:06,817 --> 00:04:08,747
<b>Don't worry about the news and go.</b>

71
00:04:09,157 --> 00:04:11,087
<b>- I'm sorry.
- Hey.</b>

72
00:04:11,557 --> 00:04:13,826
<b>I told you to hurry over.
Why are you here?</b>

73
00:04:13,826 --> 00:04:15,856
<b>- Do you think I'm a joke?
- That's enough!</b>

74
00:04:16,226 --> 00:04:18,027
<b>Why do you always tell me to stop?</b>

75
00:04:18,027 --> 00:04:19,426
<b>What's with you two?</b>

76
00:04:19,426 --> 00:04:20,766
<b>I told you to stop.</b>

77
00:04:21,666 --> 00:04:23,736
<b>- What's wrong?
- Hurry up and go.</b>

78
00:04:24,166 --> 00:04:25,166
<b>Yes, ma'am.</b>

79
00:04:28,267 --> 00:04:29,306
<b>What's going on?</b>

80
00:04:29,707 --> 00:04:30,806
<b>What is it?</b>

81
00:04:31,337 --> 00:04:33,507
<b>Shouldn't he be preparing
for the news?</b>

82
00:04:33,676 --> 00:04:35,707
<b>Jeong Hoon won't be able
to read the news today,</b>

83
00:04:36,847 --> 00:04:38,017
<b>so tell Reporter Cha to do it.</b>

84
00:04:38,017 --> 00:04:39,887
<b>I'm his team leader!</b>

85
00:04:39,887 --> 00:04:42,447
<b>So why can't you tell me
why he can't do it?</b>

86
00:04:42,447 --> 00:04:43,816
<b>Actually,</b>

87
00:04:44,856 --> 00:04:47,387
<b>Ha Jin was abducted by her stalker.</b>

88
00:04:48,257 --> 00:04:49,827
<b>- What?
- The police is investigating it...</b>

89
00:04:49,827 --> 00:04:52,197
<b>behind the closed doors,
so we'll have to wait and see.</b>

90
00:04:52,197 --> 00:04:55,626
<b>Darn it! What kind of a lunatic
would do something like that?</b>

91
00:05:44,277 --> 00:05:47,287
<b>Really? Okay, I'll call you back.</b>

92
00:05:47,287 --> 00:05:48,587
<b>- Sir.
- Yes?</b>

93
00:05:48,686 --> 00:05:50,957
<b>Moon Chul lied about
having a drink with a friend...</b>

94
00:05:50,957 --> 00:05:52,926
<b>on the day
of the motorcycle accident.</b>

95
00:05:52,926 --> 00:05:53,926
<b>What?</b>

96
00:05:53,926 --> 00:05:55,827
<b>He wasn't picking up his phone
since yesterday.</b>

97
00:05:55,827 --> 00:05:57,957
<b>I just talked to that friend,</b>

98
00:05:57,957 --> 00:05:59,767
<b>and he said the last time
the two met was over a week ago.</b>

99
00:05:59,767 --> 00:06:02,327
<b>Darn it. I knew
something was fishy about him.</b>

100
00:06:03,666 --> 00:06:06,407
<b>I think it was his doing.</b>

101
00:06:06,467 --> 00:06:07,537
<b>Hold on.</b>

102
00:06:09,637 --> 00:06:10,777
<b>It's Ji Hyun Geun.</b>

103
00:06:13,106 --> 00:06:14,147
<b>Hello?</b>

104
00:06:15,676 --> 00:06:17,147
<b>I just got in touch
with Ji Hyun Geun.</b>

105
00:06:17,816 --> 00:06:20,986
<b>According to him, he was
at his studio since last night.</b>

106
00:06:21,186 --> 00:06:22,686
<b>I'm going there right now to check.</b>

107
00:06:25,287 --> 00:06:27,626
<b>We're sorry for disturbing you
when you must be busy.</b>

108
00:06:27,626 --> 00:06:28,757
<b>Thank you for your cooperation.</b>

109
00:06:28,757 --> 00:06:31,796
<b>Not at all.
I'm sorry I didn't pick up sooner.</b>

110
00:06:31,957 --> 00:06:33,726
<b>I'll answer my phone on time
from now on,</b>

111
00:06:33,726 --> 00:06:34,866
<b>so call me
whenever you need my help.</b>

112
00:06:34,866 --> 00:06:36,936
<b>- Okay.
- Goodbye.</b>

113
00:06:50,447 --> 00:06:51,777
<b>How did it go?</b>

114
00:06:51,876 --> 00:06:53,447
<b>We looked around,</b>

115
00:06:53,447 --> 00:06:55,046
<b>but we couldn't find
anything suspicious.</b>

116
00:06:55,847 --> 00:06:57,116
<b>I see.</b>

117
00:06:57,116 --> 00:07:00,986
<b>It's become highly likely
that Moon Chul is the culprit.</b>

118
00:07:01,887 --> 00:07:04,657
<b>Once we dig deeper,
we'll be able to find a lead.</b>

119
00:07:04,657 --> 00:07:06,226
<b>- So please be patient.
- Okay.</b>

120
00:07:06,226 --> 00:07:09,666
<b>Did you not receive
any suspicious calls?</b>

121
00:07:10,267 --> 00:07:12,337
<b>No, I didn't.</b>

122
00:07:12,436 --> 00:07:15,967
<b>If you do receive any in the future,</b>

123
00:07:15,967 --> 00:07:17,577
<b>please let us know.</b>

124
00:07:17,907 --> 00:07:19,007
<b>All right. I'll do that.</b>

125
00:07:19,007 --> 00:07:20,847
<b>- All right. Goodbye.
- Goodbye.</b>

126
00:07:44,837 --> 00:07:45,837
<b>Stop.</b>

127
00:07:47,267 --> 00:07:50,077
<b>I got you, you rat.</b>

128
00:07:50,507 --> 00:07:52,436
<b>Isn't this enough evidence?</b>

129
00:07:52,676 --> 00:07:55,147
<b>Request for an emergency warrant...</b>

130
00:07:55,147 --> 00:07:56,476
<b>and put out an APB for Moon Chul.</b>

131
00:07:56,476 --> 00:07:58,416
<b>Find out which way he drove...</b>

132
00:07:58,416 --> 00:07:59,847
<b>and get his credit card activity.</b>

133
00:07:59,847 --> 00:08:00,847
<b>- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.</b>

134
00:08:03,587 --> 00:08:04,657
<b>Ha Kyung.</b>

135
00:08:05,356 --> 00:08:06,356
<b>Ms. Park.</b>

136
00:08:08,657 --> 00:08:10,556
<b>Are you okay?
Do you want some water?</b>

137
00:08:11,626 --> 00:08:14,397
<b>Did the police call?</b>

138
00:08:16,337 --> 00:08:17,637
<b>No.</b>

139
00:08:23,806 --> 00:08:24,976
<b>Hello, detective.</b>

140
00:08:26,507 --> 00:08:28,707
<b>Chul was at the scene?</b>

141
00:08:29,347 --> 00:08:31,246
<b>Are you saying he's the culprit?</b>

142
00:08:34,616 --> 00:08:37,857
<b>Okay, I'll be waiting for your call.
Goodbye.</b>

143
00:08:39,086 --> 00:08:42,556
<b>Is it Chul?
Did he really abduct her?</b>

144
00:08:43,426 --> 00:08:45,027
<b>They're not certain yet.</b>

145
00:08:45,627 --> 00:08:47,527
<b>They're going
to search his house first.</b>

146
00:08:47,527 --> 00:08:50,096
<b>Oh, dear. Poor Ha Jin.</b>

147
00:08:50,966 --> 00:08:52,637
<b>She must be terrified.</b>

148
00:09:49,627 --> 00:09:50,926
<b>- Open it.
- Yes, sir.</b>

149
00:09:58,537 --> 00:09:59,806
<b>There's no one here.</b>

150
00:09:59,966 --> 00:10:01,706
<b>I think it's been vacant
for some time.</b>

151
00:10:03,436 --> 00:10:05,737
<b>What? These are all luxury items.</b>

152
00:10:06,107 --> 00:10:07,206
<b>Really?</b>

153
00:10:07,206 --> 00:10:09,277
<b>I'm sure managers don't earn
hefty wages.</b>

154
00:10:09,946 --> 00:10:11,617
<b>- Did you find anything?
- No, sir.</b>

155
00:10:15,517 --> 00:10:16,686
<b>What is this?</b>

156
00:10:19,416 --> 00:10:20,556
<b>What is this?</b>

157
00:10:20,556 --> 00:10:23,027
<b>What? It's an earring.</b>

158
00:11:32,326 --> 00:11:33,466
<b>Don't you know me?</b>

159
00:11:34,926 --> 00:11:37,696
<b>We met several times with Seo Yeon.</b>

160
00:11:38,566 --> 00:11:41,966
<b>Who is this? Why are you
answering Seo Yeon's phone?</b>

161
00:11:43,037 --> 00:11:44,907
<b>Jeong Hoon, save me.</b>

162
00:11:44,907 --> 00:11:47,076
<b>- Save me, Jeong Hoon!
- Are you okay, Seo Yeon?</b>

163
00:11:47,076 --> 00:11:49,007
<b>- Jeong Hoon!
- Seo Yeon?</b>

164
00:11:49,007 --> 00:11:50,977
<b>Please get yourself together,
Seo Yeon!</b>

165
00:11:51,147 --> 00:11:52,316
<b>You scumbag.</b>

166
00:11:53,416 --> 00:11:54,416
<b>Jeong Hoon.</b>

167
00:11:54,416 --> 00:11:56,357
<b>This is all your fault.</b>

168
00:11:56,357 --> 00:11:58,357
<b>Seo Yeon changed all because of you.</b>

169
00:11:59,157 --> 00:12:03,997
<b>It's all your fault, Lee Jeong Hoon!</b>

170
00:12:16,806 --> 00:12:17,907
<b>Hey, Tae Eun.</b>

171
00:12:19,037 --> 00:12:22,346
<b>Are you saying her stalker
mimicked Moon Seong Ho?</b>

172
00:12:23,377 --> 00:12:27,086
<b>I think he became more aggressive
as he met with Moon Seong Ho.</b>

173
00:12:30,657 --> 00:12:33,157
<b>Had it not been for me,
he would've never known about him.</b>

174
00:12:34,186 --> 00:12:36,357
<b>Then none of this would've happened.</b>

175
00:12:36,357 --> 00:12:37,826
<b>Don't blame yourself.</b>

176
00:12:37,826 --> 00:12:39,096
<b>Even if you weren't involved,</b>

177
00:12:39,096 --> 00:12:40,727
<b>scumbags like him
would've found a way.</b>

178
00:12:41,566 --> 00:12:43,566
<b>You're also a victim,
so don't be ridiculous.</b>

179
00:12:45,566 --> 00:12:47,436
<b>Didn't you say the police
were after her manager?</b>

180
00:12:47,666 --> 00:12:50,637
<b>Now that they know their target,
he'll get caught soon.</b>

181
00:12:52,306 --> 00:12:54,477
<b>There's something unsettling
about Director Ji.</b>

182
00:12:55,277 --> 00:12:56,576
<b>What do you mean?</b>

183
00:12:57,477 --> 00:12:59,416
<b>It's hard to explain.</b>

184
00:13:00,316 --> 00:13:01,716
<b>But I've always felt this way.</b>

185
00:13:02,617 --> 00:13:05,186
<b>He reminds me of Moon Seong Ho.</b>

186
00:13:07,127 --> 00:13:10,127
<b>After seeing Moon Seong Ho recently,
this feeling became even stronger.</b>

187
00:13:10,426 --> 00:13:11,826
<b>Did you tell this to the police?</b>

188
00:13:14,267 --> 00:13:15,966
<b>It's just a feeling that I have.</b>

189
00:13:18,267 --> 00:13:20,737
<b>If all the evidence they found
point to Moon Chul,</b>

190
00:13:20,737 --> 00:13:22,267
<b>then he must be the culprit.</b>

191
00:13:25,176 --> 00:13:27,576
<b>Is this Ms. Yeo's earring?</b>

192
00:13:28,676 --> 00:13:29,816
<b>Are you looking for something?</b>

193
00:13:29,946 --> 00:13:31,576
<b>I can't find the other one.</b>

194
00:13:31,576 --> 00:13:33,117
<b>Didn't you keep them together?</b>

195
00:13:33,316 --> 00:13:35,216
<b>I thought I did,
but I can't find one of them.</b>

196
00:13:37,686 --> 00:13:38,956
<b>This would've been perfect.</b>

197
00:13:39,926 --> 00:13:42,987
<b>Yes, it is. She lost it a while ago.</b>

198
00:13:43,997 --> 00:13:45,627
<b>We found it at Moon Chul's place.</b>

199
00:13:46,326 --> 00:13:49,027
<b>He must've been sneaking
into your house for some time now.</b>

200
00:13:50,637 --> 00:13:53,206
<b>We were like family,
so it must've been easy.</b>

201
00:13:53,836 --> 00:13:55,737
<b>He knew the passcode as well.</b>

202
00:13:57,777 --> 00:13:59,407
<b>How dare he?</b>

203
00:13:59,407 --> 00:14:01,446
<b>Ma'am.</b>

204
00:14:01,576 --> 00:14:04,647
<b>Is there anything you know
about his family...</b>

205
00:14:04,647 --> 00:14:06,686
<b>or his close friends?</b>

206
00:14:06,787 --> 00:14:08,787
<b>Do you know whom he'd visit
during this situation?</b>

207
00:14:10,117 --> 00:14:12,086
<b>He said his parents lived
in Gangwon Province.</b>

208
00:14:12,257 --> 00:14:15,086
<b>He said it was a very rural area
and that I wouldn't know.</b>

209
00:14:15,956 --> 00:14:18,027
<b>He could be hiding there.</b>

210
00:14:18,027 --> 00:14:21,666
<b>Call his parents and ask
if he has contacted them recently.</b>

211
00:14:21,767 --> 00:14:22,767
<b>Yes, sir.</b>

212
00:14:33,676 --> 00:14:35,846
<b>Don't get the wrong idea.</b>

213
00:14:36,676 --> 00:14:39,076
<b>Seo Yeon loves me.</b>

214
00:14:39,887 --> 00:14:42,416
<b>(Don't get the wrong idea.
Ha Jin loves me.)</b>

215
00:14:42,686 --> 00:14:44,556
<b>- Bye.
- Goodbye.</b>

216
00:15:13,076 --> 00:15:15,287
<b>(Directed and written
by Ji Hyun Geun)</b>

